title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Lunar New Year Stunt Races
content:
The Grand Senora Desert is stunning, doubly so when the sky above is filled with fireworks and tuned-up vehicles spiked with nitrous oxide. Ring in the Year of the Horse with a vulgar display of horsepower in The Senora Derby, a new Lunar New Year Stunt Race for sports vehicles set in the arid expanse above Los Santos.

This and all other Lunar New Year Stunt Races are paying out 3X GTA$ and RP for the next two weeks as part of the Featured Series.
